{"id":775,"date":"2022-05-11T17:55:57","date_gmt":"2022-05-11T17:55:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/new.zsmarianske.cz\/?page_id=775"},"modified":"2022-08-25T21:01:52","modified_gmt":"2022-08-25T21:01:52","slug":"profil-skoly","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/o-skole\/profil-skoly\/","title":{"rendered":"Profil \u0161koly"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class='flex_column av-70dh3-6a044b183d61ce258ba862d3dc0bc1ec av_one_full  avia-builder-el-0  el_before_av_icon_box  avia-builder-el-first  first flex_column_div '   ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-l362f17w-bcc21056100837e3e27fa6467b5d5237'  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><h1>Profil \u0161koly<\/h1>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-cyfhr-01c820705f66a2fddfcd039479ea6ccb\">\n.iconbox.av-cyfhr-01c820705f66a2fddfcd039479ea6ccb .iconbox_icon{\ncolor:#f474a1;\n}\n<\/style>\n<article  class='iconbox iconbox_left av-cyfhr-01c820705f66a2fddfcd039479ea6ccb  avia-builder-el-2  el_after_av_one_full  el_before_av_icon_box '  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class=\"iconbox_content\"><header class=\"entry-content-header\"><a href='https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/kronika-skoly.pdf' title='Kronika \u0161koly'  target=\"_blank\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"iconbox_icon heading-color\" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='\ue84f' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'><\/a><h3 class='iconbox_content_title '  itemprop=\"headline\" ><a href='https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/kronika-skoly.pdf' title='Kronika \u0161koly'  target=\"_blank\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kronika \u0161koly<\/a><\/h3><\/header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop=\"text\" ><\/div><\/div><footer class=\"entry-footer\"><\/footer><\/article>\n\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-l362bfuf-74a8278ef48431e73d216a28704e9ad1\">\n.iconbox.av-l362bfuf-74a8278ef48431e73d216a28704e9ad1 .iconbox_icon{\ncolor:#f474a1;\n}\n<\/style>\n<article  class='iconbox iconbox_left av-l362bfuf-74a8278ef48431e73d216a28704e9ad1  avia-builder-el-3  el_after_av_icon_box  el_before_av_textblock '  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class=\"iconbox_content\"><header class=\"entry-content-header\"><a href='https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/o-skole\/profil-skoly\/historie-skoly\/' title='Historie'  class=\"iconbox_icon heading-color\" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='\ue84f' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'><\/a><h3 class='iconbox_content_title '  itemprop=\"headline\" ><a href='https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/o-skole\/profil-skoly\/historie-skoly\/' title='Historie' >Historie<\/a><\/h3><\/header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop=\"text\" ><\/div><\/div><footer class=\"entry-footer\"><\/footer><\/article>\n<section  class='av_textblock_section av-l35lreip-8a4ce2100f7cb904b9b740356b1530ff'  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><blockquote>\n<p><span id=\"page3R_mcid1\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Na\u0161e vize:<\/strong> &#8222;Tvo\u0159iv\u00e1 \u0161kola, br\u00e1na do \u017eivota na\u0161ich d\u011bt\u00ed&#8220;<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span id=\"page3R_mcid2\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>N\u00e1\u0161<\/strong><\/span><strong> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">vzd\u011bl\u00e1vac\u00ed program:<\/span><\/strong> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">\u0160VP ZV<\/span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">\u201c<\/span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Br\u00e1na do \u017eivota\u201d<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<h3><span id=\"page3R_mcid3\" class=\"markedContent\"><br role=\"presentation\" \/><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Charakteristika \u0161koly<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>22 t\u0159\u00edd (10 t\u0159\u00edd 1. stupn\u011b, 12 t\u0159\u00edd 2. stupn\u011b)<\/li>\n<li>\u0160kola ur\u010den\u00e1 K\u00da Zl\u00edn jako \u0161kola zaji\u0161\u0165uj\u00edc\u00ed v\u00fduku \u010desk\u00e9ho jazyka pro d\u011bti cizinc\u016f<\/li>\n<li><strong>Voliteln\u00e9 p\u0159edm\u011bty:<\/strong> etick\u00e1 v\u00fdchova, cvi\u010den\u00ed z\u00a0matematiky, spole\u010denskov\u011bdn\u00fd a p\u0159\u00edrodov\u011bdn\u00fd semin\u00e1\u0159, konverzace anglick\u00e9ho jazyka<\/li>\n<li>Pos\u00edlen\u00e1 v\u00fduka \u010desk\u00e9ho jazyka v\u00a06., 7. ro\u010dn\u00edku v\u00fdukou v\u00a0d\u011blen\u00fdch skupin\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>V\u00fduka AJ od 2. t\u0159\u00eddy, 2. ciz\u00edho jazyka od 7. t\u0159\u00eddy \u2013 nab\u00eddka n\u011bmeck\u00e9ho a rusk\u00e9ho jazyka<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nab\u00eddka krou\u017ek\u016f v\u00a0r\u00e1mci \u0161koln\u00ed dru\u017einy a \u0161koln\u00edho klubu<\/strong> se zam\u011b\u0159en\u00edm na sportovn\u00ed vy\u017eit\u00ed, komunikaci a spolupr\u00e1ci: sportovn\u00ed krou\u017eky v\u00a0r\u00e1mci \u0160D, krou\u017eek sebeobrany a juda pro \u017e\u00e1ky 2. stupn\u011b, multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed krou\u017eek \u2013 tvorba videodokument\u016f, spolupr\u00e1ce s\u00a0\u010cT D\u00e9\u010dko v\u00a0r\u00e1mci \u0161koln\u00ed televize, knihovnick\u00fd krou\u017eek, Peer aktivist\u00e9 s\u00a0d\u016frazem na preventivn\u00ed programy pro \u017e\u00e1ky 1. stupn\u011b<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nab\u00eddka dou\u010dov\u00e1n\u00ed v\u00a0r\u00e1mci projekt\u016f M\u0160MT a OP VVV <\/strong>pro \u017e\u00e1ky 1., 2. stupn\u011b<\/li>\n<li><strong>P\u0159\u00edprava na p\u0159ij\u00edmac\u00ed zkou\u0161ky na S\u0160 pro \u017e\u00e1ky 9. t\u0159\u00edd <\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>5 odd\u011blen\u00ed \u0161koln\u00ed dru\u017einy <\/strong>pro \u017e\u00e1ky 1. \u2013 5. t\u0159\u00edd<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u0160koln\u00ed j\u00eddelna <\/strong>v\u00a0budov\u011b \u0161koly s\u00a0v\u00fdb\u011brem 2 j\u00eddel<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><\/h3>\n<h3><span id=\"page3R_mcid10\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Materi\u00e1ln\u00ed vybaven\u00ed \u0161koly<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Odborn\u00e9 u\u010debny <\/strong>informatiky, ciz\u00edch jazyk\u016f, biologie, fyziky, chemie, v\u00fdtvarn\u00e9 v\u00fdchovy, d\u00edlen<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u0160koln\u00ed klub s\u00a0knihovnou <\/strong>pro 1. stupe\u0148 a mimo\u0161koln\u00ed aktivity (dramatickou a hudebn\u00ed v\u00fdchovu)<\/li>\n<li><strong>Specializovan\u00e9 pracovi\u0161t\u011b \u0161koln\u00ed psycholo\u017eky a speci\u00e1ln\u00ed pedago\u017eky: <\/strong>logopedick\u00e1 p\u00e9\u010de, relaxa\u010dn\u00ed m\u00edstnost Snoozelen, pracovi\u0161t\u011b \u0161koln\u00ed psycholo\u017eky, u\u010debna pro \u017e\u00e1ky, vy\u017eaduj\u00edc\u00edmi speci\u00e1ln\u00ed pedagogickou p\u00e9\u010di<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nov\u00e9 multifunk\u010dn\u00ed \u0161koln\u00ed h\u0159i\u0161t\u011b <\/strong>v\u00a0are\u00e1lu \u0161koly s\u00a0hern\u00edmi prvky pro \u0161koln\u00ed dru\u017einu<\/li>\n<li><strong>Sportovn\u00ed hala v\u00a0bl\u00edzkosti \u0161koly <\/strong>a 2 men\u0161\u00ed t\u011blocvi\u010dny v\u00a0budov\u011b \u0161koly<\/li>\n<li><strong>U\u010debna v\u00fdtvarn\u00e9 v\u00fdchovy <\/strong>s\u00a0keramickou d\u00edlnou, vybavenou keramickou pec\u00ed a hrn\u010d\u00ed\u0159sk\u00fdmi kruhy<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u0160koln\u00ed d\u00edlny, <\/strong>nov\u011b vybaven\u00e9 stroji a pom\u016fckami pro pr\u00e1ci se d\u0159evem a dal\u0161\u00edmi materi\u00e1ly<\/li>\n<li><strong>Odborn\u00e9 u\u010debny a kmenov\u00e9 t\u0159\u00eddy <\/strong>vybaven\u00e9 modern\u00ed ICT technikou (interaktivn\u00ed tabule, keramick\u00e9 tabule, PC, dataprojektory, vizualiz\u00e9ry), ve t\u0159\u00edd\u00e1ch 1. stupn\u011b a odborn\u00fdch u\u010debn\u00e1ch 2. stupn\u011b jsou pro \u017e\u00e1ky k\u00a0dispozici tablety<\/li>\n<li><strong>U\u010debna informatiky <\/strong>vybaven\u00e1 nov\u00fdmi robotick\u00fdmi pom\u016fckami pro v\u00fduku ICT od 4. do 9. t\u0159\u00eddy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span id=\"page3R_mcid13\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Spolupr\u00e1ce s rodi\u010di<\/span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">v r\u00e1mci organizace IRP\u0160<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ve \u0161kole je dlouholetou tradic\u00ed nadstandardn\u00ed spolupr\u00e1ce s\u00a0organizac\u00ed rodi\u010d\u016f IRP\u0160. Spole\u010dn\u011b pravideln\u011b \u0161kola a rodi\u010de organizuj\u00ed:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"page3R_mcid14\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">V<\/span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">\u00e1no\u010dn\u00ed a<\/span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">V<\/span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">elikono\u010dn\u00ed d\u00edlny<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span id=\"page3R_mcid14\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Den d\u011bt\u00ed s M\u0160 Ol\u0161ava<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li>\u0160koln\u00ed sb\u011br pap\u00edru <strong>\u2013 <\/strong>podpora ekologick\u00e9 v\u00fdchovy a \u0161koln\u00ed knihovny n\u00e1kupem nov\u00fdch knih<\/li>\n<li>Tvo\u0159iv\u00e9 d\u00edlny<\/li>\n<li>P\u0159iv\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed prv\u0148\u00e1\u010dk\u016f a rozlou\u010den\u00ed s\u00a0dev\u00e1\u0165\u00e1ky<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span id=\"page3R_mcid16\" class=\"markedContent\"><\/span><span id=\"page3R_mcid17\" class=\"markedContent\"><br role=\"presentation\" \/><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Co nab\u00edz\u00edme nav\u00edc<\/span><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Dlouholet\u00e1 tradice v\u00fdm\u011bnn\u00fdch t\u00fddenn\u00edch pobyt\u016f \u017e\u00e1k\u016f na\u0161\u00ed \u0161koly a n\u011bmeck\u00e9 \u0161koly v\u00a0Kranichfeldu<\/li>\n<li>Dlouholet\u00e1 spolupr\u00e1ce na projektu \u0160kola \u0161kole \u2013 Nadace Bez m\u00e1my: podpora \u0161koly v\u00a0Simike v Tanz\u00e1nii<\/li>\n<li>Pravideln\u00e1 p\u00e9\u010de o \u017e\u00e1ky se speci\u00e1ln\u00edmi vzd\u011bl\u00e1vac\u00edmi pot\u0159ebami a talentovan\u00e9 \u017e\u00e1ky v r\u00e1mci \u0161koln\u00edho poradensk\u00e9ho pracovi\u0161t\u011b: \u0161koln\u00ed v\u011bdeck\u00e1 konference, logopedie, dou\u010dov\u00e1n\u00ed, slu\u017eby \u0161koln\u00ed psycholo\u017eky v r\u00e1mci t\u0159\u00eddn\u00edch kolektiv\u016f i individu\u00e1ln\u00ed konzultace pro \u017e\u00e1ky a rodi\u010de, preventivn\u00ed programy v r\u00e1mci peer program\u016f, vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed relaxa\u010dn\u00ed m\u00edstnosti Snoozelen, odborn\u00e9 besedy pro rodi\u010de, kari\u00e9rov\u00e9 poradenstv\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>Zapojen\u00ed do projekt\u016f \u010clov\u011bka v\u00a0t\u00edsni \u2013 Jednoho sv\u011bta na \u0161kol\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>Preventivn\u00ed program Patron \u2013 m\u00e1m toho, kdo mn\u011b pom\u016f\u017ee pro \u017e\u00e1ky 1., 9. t\u0159\u00edd \u2013 adapta\u010dn\u00ed program<\/li>\n<li>Adapta\u010dn\u00ed programy pro \u017e\u00e1ky 1., 6. t\u0159\u00edd s\u00a0pobytem v\u00a0mimo\u0161koln\u00edm prost\u0159ed\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>Realizace projekt\u016f OP VVV, M\u0160MT, ZK<\/li>\n<li>Spolupr\u00e1ce s\u00a0\u010cT D\u00e9\u010dko v\u00a0r\u00e1mci multimedi\u00e1ln\u00edho krou\u017eku \u2013 \u0161koln\u00ed televize<\/li>\n<li>Happeningy a celo\u0161koln\u00ed projekty k\u00a0v\u00fdznamn\u00fdm v\u00fdro\u010d\u00edm \u2013 podpora v\u00fdchovy k\u00a0demokratick\u00fdm hodnot\u00e1m spole\u010dnosti<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/section>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":1148,"menu_order":21,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/775"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=775"}],"version-history":[{"count":35,"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/775\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1045,"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/775\/revisions\/1045"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1148"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zsmarianske.cz\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=775"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}